{"tid":644480,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"marvel電影戰力表現","createTime":"2018-04-27T09:09:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T21:41:14.000Z","uid":84442,"like":10,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"5584e9babc820f1864f9fc921a3c86024410950b","tid":644480,"uid":84442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:09:01.000Z","msg":"雖然我一直都係marvel fans <br />\n但係marvel電影世界一直有個通痛<br />\n就係戰鬥力既表現太低<br />\n最直觀就係英雄拳頭既破壞力<br />\n冇特效加成而且對環境破壞唔大<br />\n同時故事上一直吹到敵人毀滅星球宇宙好簡單<br />\n好似avg3咁齊石宇宙仆街<br />\n但係thomas一拳既表現上感覺完全冇力<br />\n一層樓都唔知破唔破壞到<br />\n<br />\n呢點dc電影就表現得比較好 特別係超人對決甚至破壞成個城市<br />\n表現到個張力出黎 感受到神與人既差距<br />\n當然dc唯一既優點可能得呢度<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999"},{"pid":"521c9494af6a3c47e0e4aeb2333e99aa296db7d6","tid":644480,"uid":5190,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:13:01.000Z","msg":"因為超人真係可以一拳打爆一橦樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nHulk都未必得"},{"pid":"56a9653fa226b67f5a95a848ca8a8aee73b57af5","tid":644480,"uid":70527,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:17:49.000Z","msg":"所以正義聯盟只要一個成員就得"},{"pid":"27800ad54703fe88266c17cbb788c594030e55a2","tid":644480,"uid":58630,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:18:52.000Z","msg":"Thomas <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0506a4303061014e00bee3f9d5cc7afc160398b7","tid":644480,"uid":74778,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:19:05.000Z","msg":"因為Marvel無諗過要表達d乜"},{"pid":"f5e2eb063468780b4d7f6f9606c49bfb126e754c","tid":644480,"uid":123497,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T09:20:30.000Z","msg":"根本成出戲d人物都nerfs晒"},{"pid":"942ff7bd25cd680de11fad50d67f6efff9c08461","tid":644480,"uid":1330,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"27800ad54703fe88266c17cbb788c594030e55a2","tid":644480,"uid":58630,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-2